      <p className="text-gray-600 text-lg">
        Eventify is a club management platform designed to streamline event organization,
        resource booking, and communication. Managing college events can be challenging â€” from coordinating venues and resources to tracking attendance and engagement.
        Eventify simplifies this process by offering an intuitive interface 
      </p>
      <br></br>
      <br></br>
      <h2 className="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p className="text-gray-600 text-lg">Our goal is to reduce the manual effort in managing events and foster greater student engagement by providing an interactive, secure, and scalable platform.
